{"tid":343260,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"讀UCEM轉行，有無人都想轉行做測量？","createTime":"2017-08-01T09:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T13:40:25.000Z","uid":71374,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48a62a7f7fff45e5ab787fc8178777e58c94b962","tid":343260,"uid":71374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:55:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://icdfl.com/cem/index-zh.html?gclid=CIjxwu_gtdUCFVJ_vQodTdsIiw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ficdfl.com%2Fcem%2Findex-zh.html%3Fgclid%3DCIjxwu_gtdUCFVJ_vQodTdsIiw&d=zyqxBc1rL4iI1hgoV0o7wr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=65df4ac9\" target=\"_blank\">http://icdfl.com/cem/index-zh.html?gclid=CIjxwu_gtdUCFVJ_vQodTdsIiw</a><br />\n<br />\nUCEM的碩士課程均為轉換課程，專為非相關學士學位持有人而設，適合希望加入建築、測量及房地產行業人仕報讀，完成課程後可考取多個學會專業會藉，<span style=\"color: red;\">成為持牌測量師！<br />\n</span><br />\n工料測量學理碩士 <br />\n<br />\n房地產學理碩士 <br />\n<br />\n建築測量學理碩士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">UCEM學士及碩士課程畢業生均可申請香港測量師學會見習測量師會藉，課程均獲得以下多個學會認可。<br />\n</span><br />\n香港測量師學會<br />\nThe Hong Kong Institute of Surveyors(HKIS)<br />\n<br />\n香港營造師學會<br />\nThe Hong Kong Institute of Construction Managers(HKICM)<br />\n<br />\n英國皇家特許測量師學會<br />\nThe Royal Institution of Chartered Surveyors (RICS)<br />\n<br />\n英國皇家特許建造學會<br />\nThe Chartered Institute of Building(CIOB)<br />\n<br />\n英國建造工程師協會<br />\nChartered Association of Building Engineers(CABE)"},{"pid":"3a4d7d23722dfb826ce60e2d3946ef0e7703272d","tid":343260,"uid":45850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:19:15.000Z","msg":"想乞米？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3ed40beeb01b05320381e4127058eb491b1e6f","tid":343260,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://icdfl.com/cem/images/terri1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ficdfl.com%2Fcem%2Fimages%2Fterri1.JPG&h=878d0226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10fd4240899463dc3de25e0788ad53de2a0817d","tid":343260,"uid":71374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T09:12:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想乞米？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解咁講？建築呢行應該幾好架？"},{"pid":"c5b29c1e48aa75f096e5870122285334e899d8ae","tid":343260,"uid":121742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T09:21:50.000Z","msg":"轉你老母測量咩"},{"pid":"b2925f5a1402f40000c5138bf7f81cd604f4bf2d","tid":343260,"uid":71374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T09:28:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉你老母測量咩</blockquote><br />\n？"},{"pid":"a408329de8c4429e3bf6a36a22bfaf42b9ecc67f","tid":343260,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T09:31:08.000Z","msg":"QS 定 BS好d?<br />\n<br />\n要幾錢讀？"},{"pid":"f6b983303b580052ae2eb47d926e631577af3a0c","tid":343260,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:27:57.000Z","msg":"打手又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cfac4d52cba75ea4e17ba8e8b4f5936f56e541e","tid":343260,"uid":73492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得罪講句<br />\nRmit同ucem班友<br />\n全行都知你廢"},{"pid":"1e207cdfa83420911c0a2afe2140959cfa80fb15","tid":343260,"uid":5196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:38:59.000Z","msg":"測量真有料洗撚考牌咩<br />\n你睇main con果班大粒野都唔係個個有牌<br />\n<br />\nBtw, CEM好難讀架, 同樣測量呢行都好垃圾"},{"pid":"b7c904329f9a94eb27d397d09ea23b594ee746f4","tid":343260,"uid":1255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:40:25.000Z","ms